0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"開始懷疑依條友甚至係連case都無&quot;真正&quot;處理過<br />\n可能只係做中介人負責庭外和解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2790b5074c76f524a446e2ef4f3002e26d520c","tid":412409,"uid":1858,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠老豆上位嗰個？</blockquote><br />\n有得靠老豆上位都上唔到個條廢柴repeat仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e253af1799eadd8d34570aa5624c421fbfe84b2","tid":412409,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:06:07.000Z","msg":"因師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c6fcecd248a68039f090e413c96b264d3cc53c","tid":412409,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"咩人係度轉移視線日日講何君堯？<br />\n<br />\n中大拆淘獨banner 無人提？"},{"pid":"8506a966fb9bfd8d57bcaca0f4462433e0dee66d","tid":412409,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145cf3e4c36f8163a549879822f73ee634d93d26","tid":412409,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人係度轉移視線日日講何君堯？<br />\n<br />\n中大拆淘獨banner 無人提？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">撕毀中大民主牆港獨海報者疑為該校李碩彥教授親屬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://prism.news/ShowArt.php?ref=20170923003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprism.news%2FShowArt.php%3Fref%3D20170923003&d=pLan3%2BEzrGXuMZG5Q%2Ft0saS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=da16a646\" target=\"_blank\">https://prism.news/ShowArt.php?ref=20170923003</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://prism.news/images/CUHKPROF_JPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprism.news%2Fimages%2FCUHKPROF_JPG.jpg&h=202cf991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左及右上：《明報》圖片；右下：中文大學網頁截圖<br />\n【稜鏡新聞訊】於本年9月17日(日)，一名白衣女子撕毀中文大學民主牆「香港獨立」海報，其後登上由一男子所駕駛的德國製黑色寶馬汽車離去，而該男子在離開前曾高呼責罵中大學生為「英國走狗」。<br />\n<br />\n稜鏡新聞獲得可靠資料，該名駕車男子為中文大學信息工程系李碩彥教授(Professor Li Shuo Yen Robert)。撕毀中文大學民主牆「香港獨立」海報的女子疑為李碩彥教授親屬。<br />\n<br />\n根據中文大學的資料，李碩彥教授於 1970 年獲國立台灣大學數學理學士學位，並於 1974 年獲加州大學柏克萊校區數學理學博士銜；曾分別於麻省理工學院教授應用數學（1974-76 年），以及於伊利諾大學芝加哥校區教授數學、統計學及計算機科學（1976-79 年）；後來轉投貝爾實驗室研究交換系統及工程理論。1989 年出任香港中文大學訊息工程講座教授，並於 2005 年獲委任為北京郵電大學顧問教授。<br />\n<br />\n李碩彥教授的妻子祖籍四川仁壽，擁有香港居民身份證，二人育有一名子女。<br />\n<br />\n《中國科學報》曾採訪李碩彥教授，在題為《將夢想播撒在祖國大地上》的報導中，李碩彥教授披露在美國貝爾實驗室工作時受到防範：「我是華人，做得再好也是『外人』，他們對我們防得很緊」，並且指：「中國是人力資源大國，如果通過科技手段激發我們的創造潛能，我們的國家還會不強大嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，李碩彥教授及其夥伴在2009年獲香港政府的「卓越學科領域計劃」資助超過1億元港幣，是香港政府歷史上最大一筆工科研究經費。<br />\n<br />\n稜鏡新聞嘗試聯絡李碩彥教授回應事件，惟在截稿前李教授仍未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://prism.news/images/CUHKPROF2_JPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprism.news%2Fimages%2FCUHKPROF2_JPG.jpg&h=f8532111&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e969d0f358f2b7920d7dcc6edf2542c8a409c70c","tid":412409,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n我都想有個咁既老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987ea4cb36f2a9faeb5ba45efba8850cc126b271","tid":412409,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"走後門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5995c589e839d6efcc0a06e1ce5f8a9991c224ca","tid":412409,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bced82b0f9bc19c5248435f6b7a79523c6b70062","tid":412409,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"廢物"},{"pid":"f07c678d3a7485534cb7fc7f1cde9bf30bafe508","tid